      <title>斯里兰卡议会通过法案监管在线内容</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-parliament-passes-bill-regulate-online-content-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡议会发言人宣布，周三，斯里兰卡立法者通过了一项监管在线内容的法案，反对派政界人士和活动人士表示，这项法律将压制言论自由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-parliament-passes-bill-regulate-online-content-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:59:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：泰国计划在两年内实现锂产量，增强电动汽车雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thailand-aims-lithium-output-two-years-boosting-ev-ambitions-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参与该项目的政府和公司官员表示，泰国希望在大约两年内开始从其西南部的一座矿山生产锂，从而增强其成为区域电动汽车（EV）生产中心的雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thailand-aims-lithium-output-two-years-boosting-ev-ambitions-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:10:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国反驳越南对南海争议岛屿的主张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rebuts-vietnams-claims-disputed-south-china-sea-islands-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部周三表示，中国对南海西沙群岛和南沙群岛的主权主张有“历史”支持，此前越南周末重申有足够证据证明对这些岛屿拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rebuts-vietnams-claims-disputed-south-china-sea-islands-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：中国恒大海外债券持有人集团将加入清算申请--消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-offshore-bondholder-group-join-liquidation-petition-sources-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名直接知情人士称，中国恒大的一个主要离岸债券持有人集团计划在周一香港法院的听证会上加入清算该开发商的请愿书。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-offshore-bondholder-group-join-liquidation-petition-sources-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:45:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行宣布下调存款准备金率，中国股市上涨，港股反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-stocks-bounce-after-pboc-announces-rate-rrr-cut-china-up-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行表示将下调银行存款准备金率，预计此举将提振本周早些时候市场崩盘后的市场情绪，香港股市周三创下两个多月以来最好的一天，而内地股市也出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-stocks-bounce-after-pboc-announces-rate-rrr-cut-china-up-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国提振经济信心的努力失败</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-attempts-lift-confidence-economy-fall-flat-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强上周出席达沃斯世界经济论坛，其使命是展示中国经济的正面形象并与金融精英进行交流：“投资中国市场不是风险，而是机遇。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-attempts-lift-confidence-economy-fall-flat-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即时观点：中国央行采取行动支持市场和经济</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，中国央行行长潘功胜表示，中国央行将从 2 月 5 日起削减银行必须持有的现金准备金数额，这是政策制定者加大力度支撑脆弱的经济复苏之际今年的首次削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄油鸡是谁发明的？印度法官将对全球最爱之争做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/who-invented-butter-chicken-indian-judge-rule-dispute-over-global-favourite-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄油鸡是印度在全球最知名的菜肴之一，味道鲜美，但显然也颇具争议，两家印度连锁餐厅就其起源问题在法庭上展开了斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/who-invented-butter-chicken-indian-judge-rule-dispute-over-global-favourite-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡就监管在线内容的新法律进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-votes-new-law-regulate-online-content-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡立法者将于周三就一项社交媒体监管法案进行投票，反对派政界人士和活动人士声称该法案将压制言论自由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-votes-new-law-regulate-online-content-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>低排放电力的增长预计将满足需求 - IEA</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/growth-low-emissions-power-expected-cover-demand-iea-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署（IEA）表示，风能、太阳能和核能等低排放能源产生的电力将足以满足未来三年全球需求的增长，并补充说电力部门的排放量正在下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/growth-low-emissions-power-expected-cover-demand-iea-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
